==Catalan==
===Alternative forms===
* {{l|ca|xarnec}}
===Etymology===
From {{bor|ca|es|lucharniego}} or {{m|es|nocharniego||nocturnal}}, originally applied to [[greyhound]]s. Compare {{cog|es|charnego}}.
===Pronunciation===
