===Noun===
{{ca-noun|m|f=xarnega}}
# {{lb|ca|often|_|derogatory}} A person who is half [[Catalan]] and half from another ethnolinguistic group.
# {{lb|ca|often|_|derogatory}} A [[Spanish]] person who lives in [[Catalonia]] but immigrated from another part of Spain and cannot speak Catalan.
